Genovian梨子市场欣欣向荣...
The Genovian pear market is blossoming...

1116
00:55:14,110 --> 00:55:15,900
这是双关语
if you'll pardon the pun.

1117
00:55:34,290 --> 00:55:37,390
那就是他们的公主
And that's their princess.

1118
00:55:38,900 --> 00:55:41,020
他们长的真快啊 是吧?
They grow up so fast, don't they?

1119
00:55:41,100 --> 00:55:42,570
嗨 你想见我?
Hi. You wanted to see me?

1120
00:55:42,600 --> 00:55:43,830
一切正常吧?
Is everything all right?

1121
00:55:43,900 --> 00:55:46,000
呃 是 是
Um, yes, yes.

1122
00:55:46,070 --> 00:55:47,600
冰桶是怎么回事?
What was happening with the ice bucket?

1123
00:55:47,670 --> 00:55:51,670
哦 我刚才只是有点笨手笨脚的
Oh. I just had a little clumsy moment.

1124
00:55:51,710 --> 00:55:52,800
-好吧  -再见
-Ok.  -Bye.

1125
00:55:52,840 --> 00:55:55,110
对了 食物很好吃
The food's delicious, by the way.

1126
00:55:59,350 --> 00:56:01,620
在苏格兰有个女权组织...
It was for a feminist group in Scotland...

1127
00:56:01,650 --> 00:56:03,140
叫"格子馅饼"
called "Tarts for Tartan".

1128
00:56:03,190 --> 00:56:04,880
