They were a wild bunch.

1129
00:56:04,920 --> 00:56:07,120
很有激情
Very exciting.

1130
00:56:07,160 --> 00:56:08,630
谢谢
Thank you.

1131
00:56:12,500 --> 00:56:14,990
下一道菜之前清清口
Between the courses to cleanse the palate.

1132
00:56:15,070 --> 00:56:16,400
好吧?
Bien?

1133
00:56:26,540 --> 00:56:28,880
对不起 有点凉
I'm sorry. It's a little cold.

1134
00:56:28,910 --> 00:56:30,210
她不知道那是冰的
She didn't realize it was frozen.

1135
00:56:30,250 --> 00:56:31,410
我们该怎么做?
What should we do?

1136
00:56:31,450 --> 00:56:32,610
嗯 我们也应该吃那么多
Well, we should take that much, too.

1137
00:56:32,650 --> 00:56:33,780
和她一样
Just do the same thing.

1138
00:56:33,820 --> 00:56:35,810
不! 不! 太冰了!
No! No! It's cold!

1139
00:56:42,330 --> 00:56:44,300
她们就像猴子一样
They are acting like monkeys.

1140
00:56:57,240 --> 00:57:00,700
你有没有过因为吃冰太快...
Have you ever experienced that instant headache...

1141
00:57:00,750 --> 00:57:02,040
而突然感到头痛?
when you eat ice too quickly?

1142
00:57:03,780 --> 00:57:05,010
没有
No.

1143
00:57:09,450 --> 00:57:11,820
洗手
Wash your hands.

1144
00:57:21,570 --> 00:57:23,090
对不起
Excuse me.

1145
00:57:23,170 --> 00:57:25,070
我很抱歉
I'm really sorry.

1146
00:57:25,100 --> 00:57:26,400
时有发生的
It happens all the time.

1147
00:57:27,510 --> 00:57:29,800
