I would like to propose a toast...

1148
00:57:29,840 --> 00:57:33,780
祝愿Von Troken男爵和男爵夫人
to the Baroness and Baron Von Troken.

1149
00:57:33,810 --> 00:57:36,780
希望你们永远都是皇族
May you always be Baron.

1150
00:57:41,720 --> 00:57:45,247
啊 著名的Genovian梨酪甜点
Ahh, the famous Genovian pear and cheese dessert.

1151
00:57:45,291 --> 00:57:46,986
还会是别的吗?
What else?

1152
00:57:56,368 --> 00:57:57,926
...敬我们的国家
...to our country.

1153
00:57:58,003 --> 00:58:00,767
你只是穿得太讲究 喝醉了...
You are nothing but an overdressed, drunken...

1154
00:58:00,806 --> 00:58:02,774
我出去一下!
I'm outta here!

1155
00:58:09,482 --> 00:58:12,110
哦! 我湿透了!
Oh! I am sopping!

1156
00:58:15,087 --> 00:58:16,554
是我的错吗?
Was that my fault?

1157
00:58:38,444 --> 00:58:41,811
我们到大厅里喝咖啡吧?
Shall we adjourn to the grand hall for coffee?

1158
00:58:56,262 --> 00:58:58,230
对不起我让你失望了 爸爸
Sorry I let you down, Dad.

1159
00:59:01,667 --> 00:59:04,659
晚安 Louie
Good night, Louie.

1160
00:59:12,711 --> 00:59:16,772
我刚到的时候这里简直一团糟
This place was such a mess when I first arrived.

1161
00:59:16,815 --> 00:59:19,147
我的空闲时间都尽可能花在这上面了
I've been spending every spare moment in it I can.

1162
00:59:20,653 --> 00:59:22,951
拿一个喷壶 干点有用的
Pick up one of these. Make yourself useful.

1163
00:59:22,988 --> 00:59:24,114
喷洒一下
Spray everything.

1164
00:59:24,156 --> 00:59:25,783
你不因昨天发生的事而生我的气吗?
You're not mad at me for what happened?

1165
00:59:25,824 --> 00:59:27,655
实际上 我觉得很有趣
Actually, l found it rather funny.

1166
00:59:27,693 --> 00:59:30,253
让我想起了自己的第一个皇家宴会
Reminds me of my first royal dinner party.

1167
00:59:30,296 --> 00:59:32,992
我不小心撞翻了一套铠甲...
I accidentally knocked over a suit of armor...

1168
00:59:33,032 --> 00:59:36,627
矛直接穿过了烤乳猪
and the spear went right through the suckling pig.

1169
00:59:40,406 --> 00:59:45,708
Amelia 我们今天为什么不把课程放一放...
Amelia, why don't we cancel lessons for today...

1170
00:59:45,744 --> 00:59:47,177
去玩一玩呢?
and just have some fun?

1171
00:59:47,212 --> 00:59:48,474
玩?
Fun?

1172
00:59:48,514 --> 00:59:51,278
你不是很忙吗?
You're not too busy for something like that?

1173
00:59:51,317 --> 00:59:53,979
陛下 Jerome夫人已经到了...
Your Majesty, Lady Jerome has arrived...

1174
00:59:54,019 --> 00:59:56,146
法国领事的助理在线上等着
and I have the French Consulate's assistant on hold.

1175
00:59:56,188 --> 00:59:58,156
他想确认今天的晚宴
He wants to confirm tonight's dinner.

1176
00:59:58,190 --> 00:59:59,157
帮我致歉
Send my apologies.

1177
00:59:59,191 --> 01:00:00,351
取消今天所有的安排
Cancel everything for today.

1178
01:00:00,392 --> 01:00:02,360
我要让一位真正的本地人...
I'm being shown San Francisco...

1179
01:00:02,394 --> 01:00:04,385
带我游旧金山
by a true San Franciscan.

1180
01:00:04,430 --> 01:00:06,159
告诉Joseph我要用车
Tell Joseph I'll need the car.

1181
01:00:06,198 --> 01:00:07,222
是 夫人
Yes, ma'am.

1182
01:00:07,266 --> 01:00:12,101
哦 等等! 我想让你见识一下我的宝贝
Oh, wait! I want to show you my baby.

1183
01:00:23,749 --> 01:00:26,547
我很长时间都没坐过...
I haven't sat in the front seat of a car...

1184
01:00:26,585 --> 01:00:28,485
汽车前座了
in the longest time.

1185
01:00:28,520 --> 01:00:29,817
对了...
By the way...

1186
01:00:29,855 --> 01:00:31,413
谢谢你付修车的钱 奶奶
thanks for the money for my car, Grandma.

1187
01:00:31,457 --> 01:00:33,891
嗯 你要带我去哪?
So, where are you taking me?

1188
01:00:33,926 --> 01:00:36,394
嗯 你有零钱吗?
Well, do you have any change?

1189
01:00:36,428 --> 01:00:40,330
没有 对皇室来说身上有叮当声是不合适的
No. It's not appropriate for royalty to jingle.

1190
01:00:40,366 --> 01:00:42,857
好吧 我去换零钱
OK. I'll get the change.

1191
01:00:44,269 --> 01:00:45,463
这是我最喜欢的!
This one's my favorite!

1192
01:00:45,537 --> 01:00:48,301
把钱投进去 抓住他的手
You put the quarter in and grab his hand.

1193
01:00:48,340 --> 01:00:49,807
碰那个?
I touch that?

1194
01:00:49,842 --> 01:00:50,934
是的 碰那个
Yes, you touch that.

1195
01:00:50,976 --> 01:00:52,944
