And then you press the button...

1196
01:00:52,978 --> 01:00:54,809
然后 呃...
and, uh...

1197
01:00:54,847 --> 01:00:57,247
然后就玩吧
And then you just go.

1198
01:00:57,282 --> 01:00:59,842
像Rupert在列支敦士登...
Looks like Rupert's cousin...

1199
01:00:59,885 --> 01:01:01,716
的表亲
from Liechtenstein.

1200
01:01:01,754 --> 01:01:03,119
我怎么知道开始了?
How do l know when it's ready?

1201
01:01:03,155 --> 01:01:05,214
哦 它自己会开始 开始了!
Oh, it'll just go. There you go!

1202
01:01:05,257 --> 01:01:07,851
-加油 加油 加油!  -哦!
-Go, go, go!  -Ow!

1203
01:01:07,893 --> 01:01:10,054
你甘愿受这种耻辱?
You enjoy this humiliation?

1204
01:01:10,095 --> 01:01:11,221
嗯 第一次都很难...
Well,it's hard the first time...

1205
01:01:11,263 --> 01:01:12,389
你可以再试一次
but you can do it again.

1206
01:01:12,431 --> 01:01:14,262
拿着
Hold this.

1207
01:01:14,333 --> 01:01:16,267
哦 加油! 你能做到 奶奶!
Oh, come on! You can do it, Grandma!

1208
01:01:16,301 --> 01:01:17,666
这次我准备好了!
I'm ready for you this time!

1209
01:01:17,703 --> 01:01:19,170
准备好了?
Ready?

1210
01:01:19,238 --> 01:01:20,762
加油! 加油! 加油!
Go! It's going! It's going!

1211
01:01:20,839 --> 01:01:23,000
加油 加油 加油! 就要赢了!
Go, go, go, go, go! You're doing it!

1212
01:01:23,042 --> 01:01:25,010
就要赢了! 加油! 哦 赢了!
You're doing it! Go! Oh, yes!

1213
01:01:26,311 --> 01:01:27,744
赢了! 击掌庆祝!
Got it! Give me five!

1214
01:01:27,780 --> 01:01:28,906
-击掌?  -击掌
-Five?  -Five.

1215
01:01:35,621 --> 01:01:37,680
我要一张!
I want one of these!

1216
01:01:37,723 --> 01:01:39,748
不过不是这张
Just not this one.

1217
01:01:43,295 --> 01:01:48,631
那么...我父亲一直想做王子吗?
So...did my father always want to be a prince?

1218
01:01:48,701 --> 01:01:50,498
哦 是的
Oh, yes.

1219
01:01:50,569 --> 01:01:54,437
除了有一次 大约是15年前...
Except once, about 15 years ago...

1220
01:01:54,473 --> 01:01:57,636
他严肃地考虑要放弃王位...
he seriously considered renouncing his title...

1221
01:01:57,676 --> 01:01:59,507
因为他遇见了一位可爱的画家...
because he met a lovely artist...

1222
01:01:59,545 --> 01:02:01,240
后者向他揭示了...
who showed him wonderful things...

1223
01:02:01,280 --> 01:02:03,077
关于人生...
about how life could be...

1224
01:02:03,115 --> 01:02:05,015
关于他自己无限美好的可能性
how he could be.

1225
01:02:06,051 --> 01:02:07,518
但是?
But?

1226
01:02:09,154 --> 01:02:11,952
但是他得做出决定...
But he had a decision to make...

1227
01:02:11,990 --> 01:02:13,753
没人能代替他做这个决定
and nobody could make it for him.

1228
01:02:13,792 --> 01:02:16,283
不是我...虽然很多人认为是我...
Not I...though many people thought I did...

1229
01:02:16,328 --> 01:02:17,818
其他什么人做出的
or anybody eIse.

1230
01:02:17,863 --> 01:02:21,424
Phillipe知道我的大儿子...
Phillipe knew that my firstborn...

1231
01:02:21,500 --> 01:02:23,092
他的哥哥Pierre 想放弃王位...
his brother Pierre, wanted to abdicate...

1232
01:02:23,168 --> 01:02:26,467
他最终这么做了 加入了教会
which he did, eventually, to join the church.

1233
01:02:26,505 --> 01:02:27,802
你父亲意识到...
Your father realized...

1234
01:02:27,840 --> 01:02:30,570
他对一个人...
that the love he could have for one person...

1235
01:02:30,609 --> 01:02:32,338
或者对两个人的爱...
or even two...

1236
01:02:32,377 --> 01:02:34,368
不能让他忘却自己...
could not make him forget the love...

1237
01:02:34,413 --> 01:02:37,109
对国家和人民的爱
he felt for his country and its people.

1238
01:02:38,951 --> 01:02:43,012
这是他做过的最困难的选择
It was the hardest thing he ever had to do.

1239
01:02:47,392 --> 01:02:48,882
你想吃点这个吗?
Do you want a bite of this?

1240
01:02:48,927 --> 01:02:52,863
为什么不呢?
Why not?

1241
01:02:52,898 --> 01:02:55,298
嗯 吃了
Well, here goes.

1242
01:02:58,737 --> 01:03:01,035
为什么 很好吃!
Why, it's delicious!

1243
01:03:01,073 --> 01:03:02,370
-真的?  -嗯
-Really?  -Mm-hmm.

1244
01:03:02,407 --> 01:03:05,501
哦 那好! 我再去买一个!
Oh, OK! Let's get another one!

1245
01:03:05,544 --> 01:03:08,980
这是去领事馆最近的路...
It's the fastest way back to the Consulate...

1246
01:03:09,014 --> 01:03:11,039
但是我讨厌这些上坡!
but I hate this hill!

1247
01:03:11,083 --> 01:03:13,813
我确信我开始感觉到那个玉米热狗了
I do believe I'm beginning to feel that corn dog.

1248
01:03:16,388 --> 01:03:18,913
