好 现在 使劲冲上去
Right. Now, blaze on up.

1251
01:03:22,394 --> 01:03:23,452
我...我成功了!
I...I got it!

1252
01:03:23,495 --> 01:03:25,588
-你成功了  -我成功了!
-You've got it.  -I got it!

1253
01:03:25,631 --> 01:03:27,189
你成功了!
You've got it!

1254
01:03:28,300 --> 01:03:30,063
哦! 我没成功!
Oh! I haven't got it!

1255
01:03:30,135 --> 01:03:32,365
哦-哦! Mia! 刹车!
Uh-oh! Mia! Brake!

1256
01:03:32,437 --> 01:03:34,632
刹车! 小心!
Brake! Look out!

1257
01:03:34,673 --> 01:03:36,538
在下面!
Down here!

1258
01:03:40,212 --> 01:03:42,908
9-1-1 我要报告一起交通事故
9-1-1, I need to report an accident.

1259
01:03:42,948 --> 01:03:45,280
你没听到钟声吗?!
You didn't hear the bell?!

1260
01:03:47,653 --> 01:03:48,779
他们让我在线上等着
They put me on hold.

1261
01:03:48,821 --> 01:03:50,413
哦 天哪!
Oh, for the love of God!

1262
01:03:50,455 --> 01:03:53,447
记下她们破坏公共财物
Put down destruction of public property.

1263
01:03:53,492 --> 01:03:56,086
我会的 我会的 最后 但同样严重的是...
I will, I will. And last, but not least...

1264
01:03:56,128 --> 01:03:58,119
无照驾驶
driving without a license.

1265
01:03:58,163 --> 01:04:00,757
同车还有一个45年前驾照就过期了...
Accompanied by an adult whose license expired...

1266
01:04:00,833 --> 01:04:02,630
的成年人
45 years ago.

1267
01:04:02,701 --> 01:04:04,896
我一直在跟你说 警官
I've been trying to tell you, Officer.

1268
01:04:04,970 --> 01:04:07,530
在Genovia驾照永远不会过期的
Licenses don't expire in Genovia.

1269
01:04:07,606 --> 01:04:08,698
对女王来说
Not for the queen.

1270
01:04:08,774 --> 01:04:11,208
我没有外交豁免权吗?
Don't I have diplomatic immunity?

1271
01:04:11,276 --> 01:04:13,608
你有 但是我们得把她带走
You do, but her we have to take downtown.

1272
01:04:13,645 --> 01:04:14,771
什么?
What?

1273
01:04:14,813 --> 01:04:16,178
对不起 小姐
I'm sorry, miss.

1274
01:04:16,215 --> 01:04:18,240
没关系 警官 我理解
It's all right, Officer. I understand.

1275
01:04:18,283 --> 01:04:21,013
我...
I...

1276
01:04:21,053 --> 01:04:23,715
我非常理解
I understand perfectly.

1277
01:04:23,755 --> 01:04:25,518
真的?
You do?

1278
01:04:25,557 --> 01:04:29,254
Mia 没有一个乡镇 城市 国家...
Mia, no town, no city, no country...

1279
01:04:29,294 --> 01:04:30,591
能够平稳地运行...
can function peacefully...

1280
01:04:30,629 --> 01:04:34,326
如果它的警官和驾驶机师...
if its officers and its transportation engineers...

1281
01:04:34,366 --> 01:04:36,493
不依法行事
don't follow the letter of the law.

1282
01:04:36,568 --> 01:04:38,092
为什么 如果能有两个这么优秀可敬的绅士...
Why, I wouId be proud...

1283
01:04:38,170 --> 01:04:41,435
为Genovia服务...
to have two such fine, honorable gentlemen...

1284
01:04:41,473 --> 01:04:42,770
我将深感骄傲
serving in Genovia.

1285
01:04:42,808 --> 01:04:44,241
哦 不敢当 夫人
Aw, shucks, ma'am.

1286
01:04:44,276 --> 01:04:46,767
夫人 我们没这么好
Ma'am, we're not all that.

1287
01:04:46,812 --> 01:04:49,679
哦 但你们大体上肯定是这样
Oh, but you most certainly are.

1288
01:04:49,715 --> 01:04:51,182
实际上...
As a matter of fact...

1289
01:04:51,216 --> 01:04:54,117
我想授予你们...
I would like to bestow upon you...

1290
01:04:54,152 --> 01:04:56,552
一个荣誉头衔...
the honor of the...

1291
01:04:56,588 --> 01:04:58,954
Genovian的勋章...
Genovian Order of the...

1292
01:04:58,991 --> 01:05:03,325
呃...Genovian玫瑰勋章
uh...Genovian Order of the Rose.

1293
01:05:10,235 --> 01:05:12,533
请跪下?
Would you please kneel?

1294
01:05:14,640 --> 01:05:17,575
呃...有人有军刀吗?
Um...does anybody have a sabre?

1295
01:05:17,643 --> 01:05:19,235
哦! 我有一把伞!
Oh! I've got an umbrella!

1296
01:05:19,278 --> 01:05:21,678
我有这个制动把手
I have an emergency brake.

1297
01:05:21,713 --> 01:05:24,147
这个可以 谢谢
This will do fine, thank you.

1298
01:05:24,182 --> 01:05:27,345
以Genovia皇室赋予我的...
With the power vested in me...

1299
01:05:27,386 --> 01:05:30,014
权力...
by the royal crown of Genovia...

1300
01:05:30,055 --> 01:05:31,750
